{"tid":1543754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講定先 星期日美國領事館邊個搞事就100%係鬼","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:15:45.000Z","uid":184726,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8d851d7aeedbb1cfe342aeafda029c9c833ae7","tid":1543754,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"我地唔係示威 而係去請願<br />\n對象亦唔係我地敵人<br />\n衝擊破壞等行為一d意義都冇<br />\n之前一直唔提倡捉鬼 係因為好難分辨係唔係鬼<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家有人話比你聽我係鬼 你捉唔捉？<br />\n之前比d鬼搞到咁慘 唔通放過佢地咁傻？</span></span></strong><br />\n至於捉到之後點處理 唔使我多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf9e3a56fb6f9e42758673636ff3d6c5f13f2b0","tid":1543754,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cf4f6e38ac5e17542b6d61e8a1045b208ae01da","tid":1543754,"uid":184726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40897301617c3d8c6ba497ef4b4dcd763f68f627","tid":1543754,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvi